content.rendered:
The Azure Folding Table is suitable for heavy contract use indoors and out! This item folds for easy storage.

Made with FSC Certified timber & a wrought iron frame and held in stock for delivery in 3-4 working days.

This item may require robinia treatment when delivered as well as annually.

Often used in Garden Centres, Hotels, Bistros and Restaurants, but this beautiful Azure Table can be used in any commercial venue.

This item carries our 2 year guarantee.
